item.title: Adding models problem
item.dc:creator: @recker450 recker450
item.description:
@recker450 wrote:

did you logon and said
“add models [id of model]”

example i just added an model with the id called 14000

i have added the ints
i logged onto an server
and said
add model 14000
i log off and close my client and compile
voila i have successfully damaged my cache unless i had preloaded it
anyway just logon and say
“add model @@@@”
replace @@@@ with the model id
